      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
        {description}
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
